        When and How to Withdraw a Property from the Market in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Withdrawing a property is not a failure. But it does have consequences for your agency agreement, your costs to date, and how your next campaign performs. Here's what sellers need to know.
      </p>
    </div>
